vh unit : viewport height = 1% of viewport height 
rem unit : root em, relative to font size of html element 

form element 
  - action attribute: link URL 
  - method attribute "get" or "post" determines how to send data to tthe url specified by action attribute 

block : different lines 
inline : same line

input 
  - types : text, email, password, file, number, submit (value="Submit" as well)
  - id 
    - related label has a for attribute for that id
  - required attribute 
  - minlength
  - pattern="[a-z0-5]{8,}" --> eight or more lowercase letters or digits 0 to 5

select element : container for group of option elements
option element : label for each dropdown option
  - select and option require closing tags
  - option needs a value attribute 

textarea element : like input element of type text but can receive multi-line text  and an initial number of text rows and columns 
  - placeholder attribute accepts a text value which is displayed until user starts typing 
